ch and look for our frequent updates.\n\nThe story mode in the games lets you find your way in an underground tunnel to find and rescue the king and while fighting the enemies, lead the king back to his throne.\n\n", "short_description": "Fight one to one by a Sword and a shield or take the challenge to defend yourself in an Arena or save the king in story mode with different weapons and types of enemy."}]}, "developer_name": "XZ Solutions", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://skippyapps.com/privacy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Skippy Apps PTY LTD.", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://skippyapps.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2710427532541308"}, {"id": "2691890164460465"}, {"id": "411892083130028"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["FIGHTING"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH", "GAMEPAD"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "26501519559496415"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75422395_762223355821106_5199826812587160372_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Y_08ni0MH3IQ7kNvgHMO3NE&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AImBnXq9fio9Ivk0Fa3nqOO&oh=00_AYDqQ9qCowKnYppIbpZRw_XLwT-QfU3dYhcjd7fV5hz18w&oe=66D5931C"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid": false, "display_name": "Thunder Gladiator - Sword Fighting Game", "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF", "context_category": {"context_categ